title: ELVIS PRESLEY - Don't think twice - Enero 29 1973 Las Vegas
description:
This is another Madison release, and this time they supply us the January 29th, 1973 show. The show itself is pretty good, including Sweet Caroline, that is very rare for 1973. Some of the other highlights are "Steamroller blues" (with James Burton guitarworks just being outstanding), What now my love" and a bluesy version of Hound Dog. The bonus song is a longer (edited) version of "Don&#039;t think twice" and last over 14 minutes.

So this is my last torrent for now, enjoy and help seeding
